text = "[center]
We, here at ReFridge inc., are excited to help 
you get started working. Your task is simple: 
you need to help clients use as many ingredients 
from their fridge as possible. The more satisfied 
the clients are with your help, the higher your pay 
at the end of the day will be. So put on a smile, and 
represent our company well!

For further guidance, continue reading:"
fit_content = true
scroll_active = false

